# World Cup dashboard deploy

Source repo: `Worldcup_dashboard` (Vite root `client/`).

After any change under `worldcup-dashboard/` or when syncing dashboard source:

1. In `Worldcup_dashboard`: `npm run build` (outputs `client/dist/`).
2. Copy `client/dist/*` into this repo's `worldcup-dashboard/` — keep `data/state.json`.
3. Commit and push to `main` so GitHub Pages serves the update at `/worldcup-dashboard/`.

Do not skip the build step; never edit bundled `assets/` by hand.
